    "<h1>Correlational Heatmap of Consecutive Character Pairings </h1>\n",
    "\n",
    "<img src=\"output.png\" style=\"width: 75%; height: auto;\">\n",
    "\n",
    "Generated by:\n",
    "<small>\n",
    "```python\n",
